title: Bride upstaged by photobombing whale Yahoo7 Be - Yahoo7
text:
Share Bride upstaged by photobombing whale Yahoo7 Be - Yahoo7 
There’s nothing worse than having a gatecrasher at your party but this uninvited wedding guest was the star of this couple’s big day. Close Humpback Whale Stuns Family on Boating Trip UP NEXT VIDEO 
The picture, which was posted to Imgur, has been liked over 1.3 million times since it was uploaded a few days ago and with just once glance, you’ll see why. 
The bride and groom were in the middle of saying their vows at Mystic Seaport in Mystic, Connecticut when out of nowhere a beluga whale appeared. This bride and groom were upstaged on their wedding day by a beluga whale. Photo: Imgur 
The whale seemed to have a hint of a smile on its face as it watched the loved-up couple getting married, with the reflection of the congregation visible in the glass. 
And while the couple and the celebrant seem oblivious to the fact that they have company, the image has sparked a string of hilarious memes online. 
Take a look at some of the best ones below: The image has sparked a string of hilarious memes. Photo: Imgur The bride and groom were getting married at Mystic Seaport in Mystic. Photo: Imgur This person swapped out the bride with the beluga whale. Photo: Imgur The cast of The Little Mermaid made an appearance. Photo: Imgur One person photoshopped in a lot of beluga whales. Photo: Imgur Another person swapped out the celebrant with the beluga. Photo: Imgur In this photo, the whale dressed for the occasion.
